hw2: 3D Objects and 1st person

Hours to complete: 15 hours

Evan Brookens
CSCI4229/5229 Summer 2016

Demonstrates how to draw objects in 3D.
Show a stary night with beds.

Key bindings
  m          Go from orthoganal view to 1st person 			           perspective
  a          Toggle axes
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

  *****1st person*****
  arrows     Control camera

 *****Orthoganol View*****
  arrows     Change view angle